Oh, I'm aware.

39:06.510 --> 39:08.763
I've had Carlos watching you both
for the last week.

39:09.513 --> 39:12.266
What we did is,
we put a poison pill inside the data.

39:12.350 --> 39:14.685
That way,
anyone tried to take anything out,

39:14.769 --> 39:17.396
it'd automatically be back-traced,
and that way we got a name.

39:17.980 --> 39:20.566
I got Carlos
to do a search of the suspect's office.

39:25.988 --> 39:27.073
Empty your bag.

39:28.491 --> 39:31.202
What? I don't understand.

39:32.036 --> 39:33.913
This is ridiculous.

39:34.497 --> 39:36.999
Uh, yep, fine, here.

39:40.252 --> 39:42.129
I don't know what you expect to find.

40:01.107 --> 40:02.608
I've never seen that before.

40:06.362 --> 40:08.823
Your desk is packed,
your belongings are in the lobby.

40:08.906 --> 40:12.159
No, I swear,
I had nothing to do with this.

40:12.243 --> 40:14.078
Hannah, tell them. Rajiv…

40:14.161 --> 40:17.039
We'll tell that
you left to spend time with your family.

40:17.123 --> 40:20.668
You say one word to anyone
about infiltrating our system,

40:21.210 --> 40:23.587
and I'll ruin the lives
of anyone you looked at.

40:31.887 --> 40:35.349
Hannah, a word. Close the door.

40:40.312 --> 40:43.357
-Hell of a week, huh?
-Uh, Andrew, I… I…

40:43.441 --> 40:44.859
Relax, Hannah. Breathe.

40:46.360 --> 40:48.154
How long have we been working together?

40:48.237 --> 40:49.864
Uh, almost eight years?

40:49.947 --> 40:53.951
Well, I think it's about time
for some new responsibilities.

40:54.660 --> 40:56.412
Didn't Rajiv just get the job?

40:56.495 --> 40:58.247
Yeah, as Junior VP.

40:58.330 --> 41:00.291
Now Andrew's gone,
we need a new Senior VP.

41:00.374 --> 41:01.459
Someone I can trust.

41:02.126 --> 41:03.377
Do you not want the job?

41:03.461 --> 41:06.464
No, I… Yes. Yes, I do.

41:06.547 --> 41:09.508
Pregnancy is not an issue.
Not for me. Unless it is for you.

41:11.552 --> 41:12.761
You switched to decaf.

41:13.679 --> 41:15.556
Sakura did the same when she was pregnant.

41:16.765 --> 41:17.808
Um…

41:17.892 --> 41:20.811
No, it will not affect anything.

41:20.895 --> 41:22.229
Family affects everything.

41:22.313 --> 41:24.398
Make sure it doesn't cloud your judgment.

41:24.899 --> 41:27.776
I'll have Carlos set you up
with a new security clearance.

41:28.903 --> 41:29.862
Thank you, Roger.

41:59.308 --> 42:00.684
Looks smaller every time.

42:02.186 --> 42:04.813
And the days go by faster and faster.

42:06.148 --> 42:07.149
Walk with me.

42:09.735 --> 42:11.362
-What's their story?
-Don't.

42:11.445 --> 42:14.949
Oh, come on. You used to love it.
You used to practically beg me--

42:15.032 --> 42:18.494
I'm in. Senior VP.

42:20.704 --> 42:23.707
I can get photos and key cards,
but I won't have full access.

42:24.291 --> 42:25.125
Not a concern.

42:25.709 --> 42:29.088
I can't get alarm specs or the key,
or temperature codes.

42:29.588 --> 42:32.174
-Roger keeps that to himself.
-We got the back door.

42:32.258 --> 42:34.552
You're in the right place
at the right time.

42:35.761 --> 42:38.305
-The timing's wrong.
-No, it's our only shot.

42:38.389 --> 42:39.974
You know whose bonds these are?

42:40.057 --> 42:41.976
There's no sense
in stealing from the poor.

42:42.726 --> 42:45.104
The Triplets aren't people
you can take their stuff

42:45.187 --> 42:46.397
and walk into the night.

42:46.480 --> 42:49.149
They'll find you. They'll kill you.

42:49.817 --> 42:51.569
I'm pretty good at not being found.

42:53.821 --> 42:57.157
Let's say you pull it off
and somehow don't end up dead. Then what?

42:57.241 --> 42:58.492
World's a better place.

42:59.493 --> 43:02.162
-I almost think you believe that.
-What's not to believe?

43:02.246 --> 43:04.290
Roger goes down, SLS collapses…

43:04.373 --> 43:06.750
-That's the idea.
-…along with my career.

43:07.751 --> 43:09.044
I'm not like you. I…

43:09.587 --> 43:12.464
How's it look if the vault gets cracked
after I take the job?

43:12.548 --> 43:13.632
You'll be rich.

43:19.513 --> 43:20.764
I could stop you.

43:22.725 --> 43:23.851
I know your plans.

43:23.934 --> 43:25.894
This ain't about my plans.

43:26.645 --> 43:28.439
This is about our plans.

43:28.522 --> 43:29.565
-Oh.
-Yeah, no, look.

43:29.648 --> 43:32.192
Seven years we've been talking this up.

43:32.276 --> 43:34.445
Seven years, and you don't say boo,

43:34.528 --> 43:37.197
and now we get right here,
right on the edge, and you…

43:40.826 --> 43:43.912
If there is something else going on,
something I need to know…

43:47.082 --> 43:47.916
Mm-mm.

43:48.792 --> 43:49.877
You're doing this.

43:50.878 --> 43:53.172
No, we're doing this.

44:56.026 --> 44:58.070
<i>Loyalty is worthless.</i>

44:58.779 --> 45:00.155
<i>Faith is dead.</i>

45:01.240 --> 45:04.952
<i>At the end of the day,</i>
<i>it will always come down to you</i>

45:05.536 --> 45:07.996
<i>versus the people who want what you have.</i>

45:09.164 --> 45:11.041
<i>And the only thing that matters is…</i>

45:12.334 --> 45:16.964
<i>can you manipulate them</i>
<i>better than they can manipulate you?</i>
